{"tid":1808500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[搞大佢]建制法團主席兼監警會萎員出律師信俾屋苑黃店","createTime":"2020-01-02T11:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T06:30:38.000Z","uid":73883,"like":180,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":164,"replies":[{"pid":"928a7c21e029088b03805cfb703c8614f918d817","tid":1808500,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:47:51.000Z","msg":"地點：觀塘曉麗苑<br />\n<br />\n發律師信嘅人：蘇麗珍，佢係前區議員(剛敗走卸任)、監狗會萎員、曉麗苑現任法團主席、現任貴州政協，曾經帶隊到狗屋撐警，以法團名義出律師信。<br />\n<br />\n收律師信嘅人：「優廚食品」，屋苑黃店，之前借出店鋪外牆俾人做連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n事件：事源係新上任張敏峯議員想喺屋苑搵地方做辦事處，但係受到諸多阻撓(直到而家都未搵到)，矛頭直指法團，有人睇唔過眼貼咗張大字報喺優廚連儂牆指法團隻手遮天，法團就出信俾優廚要佢地登報道歉兼俾律師費。<br />\n<br />\n而家好多街坊都好嬲，因為屋苑好多人都好憎蘇麗珍，佢仲要用法團嘅錢去出律師信！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5sv5iK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5sv5iK.jpg&h=4280e035&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DuiuLq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DuiuLq.jpg&h=6f4964ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKk9Bqr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKk9Bqr.jpg&h=1fa28574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2f43cd57f588cc3064bb9293e3e45f1e4e1da9a","tid":1808500,"uid":73883,"like":74,"dislike":4,"score":70,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"呢個就係蘇麗珍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyW49L9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyW49L9.jpg&h=cc8b3943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘇麗珍與何君堯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p270H6m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp270H6m.jpg&h=0b878008&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d59857e944c543c403a842e28d2a39582350b5fd","tid":1808500,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">含撚啦泛民打手！<br />\n［最後通牒］警告泛民重回正軌 否則勇武將會全面退場攬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808373\" data-aut